  "Factory Genesis HFM and CIDs PAIRING_SP": {
   "width": 9000,
   "height": 10140,
   "color": "rgb(183,28,19)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY IN LINE : GENESIS HFM and Customer IDs pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(250,199,160)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 15,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8730
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 75,
      "top": 1515,
      "height": 3765,
      "width": 7725
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) ENTER GENESIS MODE",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 1770,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 7710
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the GENESIS MODE is launched, then present a blank customer ID to immo antenna ( to check that the customer ID is blank, press the button\"CID blanking check\"",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 75,
      "top": 2355,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 7365
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4560,
      "top": 5400,
      "height": 4440,
      "width": 4305
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " CID TEST ",
     "color": "rgb(238,142,79)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 435,
      "height": 1020,
      "width": 3615
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7890,
      "height": 1935,
      "width": 4320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Genesis Mode Information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 5400,
      "height": 2430,
      "width": 4320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"CID pairing\" (VSC1 or VSC2 Customer ID pairing) for each customer ID to pair",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 3105,
      "height": 900,
      "width": 7470
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) Press the button \"EXIT GENESIS MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4680,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the customer ID is paired, then insert a new customer ID in the reader and press \"CID pairing\"",
