     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 75,
      "top": 1515,
      "height": 3795,
      "width": 8835
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Complete the \"additional pairing datas\" (11 bytes= not mandatory) and press the button \"ENTER GENESIS MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 1770,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the GENESIS MODE is launched, then present a blank customer ID near central antenna ( to check that the customer ID is blank, press the button\"CID blanking check\")",
     "color": "rgb(245,209,186)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
