  "Factory Rework Pairing : HFM or CID": {
   "width": 11700,
   "height": 11340,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY REWORK : HFM or Card pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2040,
      "height": 1605,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Complete the \"After Sales code\" ( 16 bytes) then press \"ENTER REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 11160
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for HFM pairing is launched, then",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Once all the customer IDs are paired, press the button \"EXIT REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 6360,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ECU information",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,166)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6720,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 2160,
      "width": 4770
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID ANALYSE - Select \"StartRoutine\" and press the button",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 1335,
      "width": 11400
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,166)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 9120,
      "height": 2160,
      "width": 6480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Rework Mode failure ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,166)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7200,
      "height": 1815,
      "width": 6480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press \"CID Pairing\" to pair a card",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 1560,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for customer ID pairing is launched, then",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5520,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press \"HFM pairing\" to pair the HFM",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 5040,
      "height": 1440,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the HFM is paired, the EXIT of the REWORK MODE is automatic. Then pair all the cards (procedure in right)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,170)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 6480,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 5280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
