  "Aftersales Pairing : CID": {
   "width": 12060,
   "height": 10980,
   "color": "rgb(0,64,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing :  CID pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(39,198,216)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11865
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 15,
      "top": 1920,
      "height": 5760,
      "width": 11985
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Approach the card to the transponder antenna and press the button \"Card Analyse\" to check its presence and status",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2400,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 9480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Complete PARAMETER_CID_PAIRING with blank IDE (8 bytes, IDE1;IDE2) and press \"Request Server CID pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2760,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select the \"SENDKEY_RESPONSE\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3360,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the \"Additional pairing data\" (optional) get the \"Server Answer\" from \"Pairing DDT2000\" and press \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4080,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the BCM is SA unlocked for card pairing, approach a blank Card to the antenna and press the button \"CID pairing\"  ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 5895,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10920
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) Repeat Step 6 for all Card to pair",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Card / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6480,
      "top": 7800,
      "height": 3000,
      "width": 4770
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Card ANALYSE - Select \"startRoutine\" and press the button",
     "color": "rgb(118,113,227)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 1200,
      "width": 11865
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 9720,
      "height": 1125,
      "width": 4950
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7770,
      "height": 1860,
      "width": 4935
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) If all Cards are paired, press \"Exit procedure\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 7440,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 8640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "!! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" on https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1410,
      "top": 1950,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 9360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial Narrow",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Input data to server:   67 11",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 3720,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 2040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
